title: The Epic Rocky Horror Collection
description:
NOTE: Due to the size of the torrent, please seed so everyone can enjoy.

A collection of Rocky Horror media.

Video: (all MP4 except "The Complete Cut", which is an AVI)
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show (Original trailer)
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show (UK version)
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show (US version)
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show (US - Audience participation audio track) - NOTE: This audio track only fully plays on the US version. On the UK version, it doesn't work during "Superheroes".
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show (UK - Richard O'Brien and Patricia Quinn audio commentary track)
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show: The Complete Cut (a fan-created extended cut, editing the deleted song "Once in a While" back in)
-Shock Treatment (Official US trailer)
-Shock Treatment (International trailer)
-Shock Treatment
-Shock Treatment (Fan club presidents audio commentary track)
-Rocky Horror Tribute Show
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show (Blu-ray release trailer)
-The Rocky Horror Glee Show

The music will be uploaded as a separate torrent because BitLord's torrent creation is being an asshole.
